=1920 1920w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design-9.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2048 2048w, https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design-9.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400 2400w\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2025/04/Untitled-design-9.png?quality=90\u0026amp;strip=all\u0026amp;crop=0%2C0%2C100%2C100\u0026amp;w=2400\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ccite\u003eGraphic: Polygon/Ana Diaz | Image source: Bethesda Game Studios/Bethesda Softworks via Polygon\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe first fence you unlock,\u003cstrong\u003e Ongar the World-Weary\u003c/strong\u003e, will also sell you lockpicks for \u003cstrong\u003e6 gold each\u003c/strong\u003e. He is located in Bruma and lives on the southwest side of town. If he’s not home, you can wait until the morning until he returns.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor more \u003cem\u003eOblivion Remastered\u003c/em\u003e guides, here’s how to \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/elder-scrolls-4-oblivion-remastered-guides/563551/level-up-how-to-leveling-system\"\u003elevel up\u003c/a\u003e, how to \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/elder-scrolls-4-oblivion-remastered-guides/565046/persuade-how-to-persuasion\"\u003epersuade\u003c/a\u003e, and how to \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/elder-scrolls-4-oblivion-remastered-guides/564277/cure-vampirism-how-to\"\u003ecure vampirism\u003c/a\u003e, or see our running lists of all \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/elder-scrolls-4-oblivion-remastered-guides/565698/factions-list-all-join\"\u003efactions\u003c/a\u003e, \u003ca href=\"https://www.polygon.com/elder-scrolls-4-oblivion-remastered-guides/565330/followers-list-all-how-to-recruit\"\u003efollowers\u003c/a\u003e, and \u003ca href=\"ht